  "text": "Example 4: There are variety of tools which are useful to examine xFitter output. This exercise uses Python with a Jupyter notebook to read the LHAPDF output from the previous xFitter example, manipulate the results, and generate comparison plots. Additionally, other tools are also available such as the Mathematica based ManeParse program [CITATION_1] .",
